properties.name: azure.maps.api.key
properties.description: The primary key for the Azure Maps service, used for geocoding

properties.name: apilayer.api.key
properties.description: The api key used by apilayer.com, which is used to get geocoding information based on IP

properties.name: google.firebase.config.file
properties.description: The file path to the 'google.firebase.config.file', used to load the firebase configuration

properties.name: google.firebase.config.appName
properties.description: The app name used to describe the app for Firebase, used as a unique key to load config
